## Protected Content Includes:
- Ukrainian air raid siren sounds
- "Пункт Незламності" (Resilience Point) models and textures
- DTEK-themed UI elements
- Generator models and sounds
- All custom icons and textures

## Why This License?
These assets represent Ukrainian cultural and wartime experience.
This license prevents their misuse in inappropriate or offensive contexts
while allowing sharing for educational and awareness purposes.

